and get the hell out of here.</i>

4
00:00:42,378 --> 00:00:45,079
<i>Right now.</i>

5
00:01:04,167 --> 00:01:05,933
Stupid--

6
00:01:05,935 --> 00:01:07,435
<i>Don't go back.</i>

7
