<i>Do not go back there.</i>

8
00:01:45,674 --> 00:01:47,341
Hey!

9
00:01:47,343 --> 00:01:48,776
Hey!

10
00:02:21,510 --> 00:02:23,377
What the hell's going on
in here?

11
00:04:50,325 --> 00:04:52,426
You stole my story.

12
00:04:54,062 --> 00:04:55,696
Well?

13
00:04:55,698 --> 00:04:59,066
I'm sorry. Do I--?

14
00:04:59,068 --> 00:05:00,901
- I don't believe I know you.
- I know that.

15
00:05:00,903 --> 00:05:04,372
That doesn't matter. I know you,
Mr. Rainey, that's what matters.

16
00:05:04,374 --> 00:05:06,540
You stole my story.

17
00:05:06,542 --> 00:05:08,876
You're mistaken.
I don't read manuscripts.

18
00:05:08,878 --> 00:05:10,878
You read this one already.

19
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,480
You stole it.

20
00:05:12,482 --> 00:05:13,947
I can assure you that I--

21
00:05:13,949 --> 00:05:15,383
I know you can.
I know that.

22
00:05:15,385 --> 00:05:17,017
I don't wanna be assured.

23
00:05:17,019 --> 00:05:18,419
If you want to
talk to someone

24
00:05:18,421 --> 00:05:21,622
about some grievance
you feel you may have,

25
00:05:21,624 --> 00:05:23,457
you can call my literary agent
in New York.

26
00:05:23,459 --> 00:05:26,360
This is between you and me.

27
00:05:29,165 --> 00:05:31,832
We don't need any outsiders,
Mr. Rainey.

28
00:05:31,834 --> 00:05:35,002
It is strictly
between you and me.

29
00:05:35,004 --> 00:05:38,172
All right, look, mister,
whoever you are,

30
00:05:38,174 --> 00:05:40,908
I don't like being accused
of plagiarism

31
00:05:40,910 --> 00:05:44,077
if that is in fact what you're
accusing me of. Chico, inside.

32
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,680
I don't blame you for not
liking it,

33
00:05:45,682 --> 00:05:47,515
but you did it.

34
00:05:47,517 --> 00:05:49,016
You stole my story.

35
00:05:49,018 --> 00:05:51,218
You're gonna have to leave.
I have nothing more to say.

36
00:05:51,220 --> 00:05:52,219
Yeah, I'll go.

37
00:05:52,221 --> 00:05:54,087
We'll talk more later.

38
00:05:54,089 --> 00:05:55,756
I'm not taking that.

39
00:05:55,758 --> 00:05:57,124
Won't do you any good

40
00:05:57,126 --> 00:06:00,194
to play games with me,
Mr. Rainey.

41
00:06:00,196 --> 00:06:01,862
This has got to be settled.

42
00:06:01,864 --> 00:06:04,865
So far as I'm concerned,
it is.

43
00:07:23,612 --> 00:07:25,446
"Sowing Season.

44
00:07:25,448 --> 00:07:26,914
John Shooter."

45
00:07:33,889 --> 00:07:35,723
Never heard of you, pal.

46
00:07:38,794 --> 00:07:40,027
Never heard of your story.

47
00:07:57,412 --> 00:07:58,979
Now,

48
00:08:01,583 --> 00:08:03,951
where was I?

49
00:08:03,953 --> 00:08:05,953
Oh.

50
00:08:05,955 --> 00:08:07,154
Oh.

51
00:08:33,482 --> 00:08:35,616
I'm open to suggestions.

52
