<i>"when your love was really all
you had,</i>

67
00:10:19,889 --> 00:10:22,122
<i>"was not much of a woman.</i>

68
00:10:22,124 --> 00:10:24,758
<i>"He, therefore, decided
to kill her.</i>

69
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,927
<i>"He would bury her in
the deep corner formed</i>

70
00:10:26,929 --> 00:10:28,128
<i>"where the house
and the barn</i>

71
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:30,397
<i>"came together
at an extreme angle.</i>

72
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:33,067
<i>"He would bury her where
his wife kept her garden.</i>

73
00:10:33,069 --> 00:10:35,402
<i>The garden she loved
more than she loved him."</i>

74
00:10:35,404 --> 00:10:37,037
Oh, shit. Oh, sh--

75
00:10:38,272 --> 00:10:39,673
Oh, thank God.

76
00:10:39,675 --> 00:10:42,109
From the sound of you,
I didn't know what to think.

77
00:10:42,111 --> 00:10:44,111
Here, let me get this.
That's my job.

78
00:10:44,113 --> 00:10:46,480
I'm terribly sorry, Mrs. Garvey.
I really am.

79
00:10:46,482 --> 00:10:47,881
I'll take care of this,
Mr. Rainey.

80
00:10:47,883 --> 00:10:49,116
Go on back to work.

81
00:10:49,118 --> 00:10:51,251
- I didn't write this.
- Oh, I thought you did.

82
00:10:51,253 --> 00:10:52,419
No, it's not mine.

83
00:10:52,421 --> 00:10:54,221
Look, it says
"John Shooter" right there.

84
00:10:54,223 --> 00:10:56,090
John Shooter.
It's not me.

85
00:10:56,092 --> 00:10:58,792
Oh, I thought
it was one of those, um,

86
00:10:58,794 --> 00:11:00,961
whatchamacallums,
pseudo-names or "-nyms."

87
00:11:00,963 --> 00:11:02,763
No.
No, I never used one.

88
00:11:02,765 --> 00:11:03,897
I've never used one.

89
00:11:03,899 --> 00:11:05,298
Oh, I can't imagine
why you would.

90
00:11:05,300 --> 00:11:08,435
I mean, hide behind
some made-up name.

91
00:11:08,437 --> 00:11:10,104
No, no.

92
00:11:10,106 --> 00:11:11,805
Mrs. Garvey,
what I'm trying to tell you

93
00:11:11,807 --> 00:11:13,774
is that someone else
wrote this story.

94
00:11:13,776 --> 00:11:15,776
Oh. Okey-dokey, then.

95
00:11:40,468 --> 00:11:41,902
<i>"A woman who would steal
your love</i>

96
